MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is used to load the data from stg_coo_intransit_inventory to slba.intransits table.
MAPPING.NAME: m_INTRANSITS

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: lookup on the EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF to extract the PLANT_NAME column.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select plant_cd as plant_cd, plant_name as plant_name, external_plant as external_plant from ( select distinct x.plant_cd as plant_cd, y.plant_name as plant_name, external_plant as external_plant from external_plant_xref x left join da.plant y on x.plant_cd=y.plant_cd union all select distinct aps_plant_cd as plant_cd, v.plant_name as plant_name,iwe_warehouse_id as external_plant from iwe_plant_xref u left join da.plant v on aps_plant_cd=plant_cd)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.STYLE_CD as STYLE_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.COLOR_CD as COLOR_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.ATTRIBUTE_CD as ATTRIBUTE_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.SIZE_CD as SIZE_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.REVISION_NO as REVISION_NO, EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SKU as EXTERNAL_SKU FROM EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SKU as EXTERNAL_SKU FROM EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF ,ITEM where EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.style_cd=ITEM.style_num and EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.color_cd= ITEM.color_code and EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.size_cd=ITEM.size_code and EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.attribute_cd=ITEM.attribution_code GROUP BY EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SKU

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This expression used to call the unconnected lookups and calculated the derivations .
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_INSTRANSISTS

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( NOT ISNULL(I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT ) and ISNULL(I_DC_DELIVERY_DT), IIF( I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT>TRUNC(SYSDATE), DATE_DIFF(I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT,TRUNC(SYSDATE),'DD')+V_DEST_WELL+V_DC_WELL, IIF(DATE_DIFF(TRUNC(SYSDATE),I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT,'DD')<=V_DEST_WELL,V_DEST_WELL-DATE_DIFF(TRUNC(SYSDATE),I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT,'DD')+V_DC_WELL,2+V_DC_WELL)), IIF(NOT ISNULL(I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT ) and NOT ISNULL(I_DC_DELIVERY_DT),V_DC_WELL,0))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_EST_DIS_PORT_GRTR_SYSDATE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(not isnull(LKP_DEST_DWELL),IIF(not isnull(I_ACT_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT), ADD_TO_DATE(I_ACT_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT,'DD',LKP_DEST_DWELL), IIF(not isnull(I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT), ADD_TO_DATE(I_EST_DISCHARGE_PORT_ARRIVE_DT,'DD',LKP_DEST_DWELL),I_DC_DUE_DATE)), I_DC_DUE_DATE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_EXPECTED_DC_ARRIVAL_DT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source Qualifier is used to extract the data from Source STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY.SKU, STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY.DC_ID, STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY.SUPPLIER_ID, STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY.INTRANSIT_QTY, STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY.MANIFESTNUM, STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY.DC_DUE_DATE FROM STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY where create_Date=(select max(create_date) from STG_COO_INTRANSIT_INVENTORY) and manifestnum is not null

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on the STG_TRANSPORTATION table to get the DAYS_IN_TRANSIT field.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STG_TRANSPORTATION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This table is used to get the fields DC_DWELL and DEST_DWELL
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_LEAD_TIME_DC_DWELL_DEST_DWELL1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT LEAD_TIMES.DEST_DWELL as DEST_DWELL, LEAD_TIMES.DC_DWELL as DC_DWELL, LEAD_TIMES.DC_REGION as DC_REGION, LEAD_TIMES.TRANSPORTATION_MODE as TRANSPORTATION_MODE, LEAD_TIMES.ORIGIN_PORT_CODE as ORIGIN_PORT_CODE, LEAD_TIMES.DESTINATION_PORT_CODE as DESTINATION_PORT_CODE FROM LEAD_TIMES

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: DC_REGION = I_DC_REGION AND TRANSPORTATION_MODE = I_TRANSPORT_MODE AND ORIGIN_PORT_CODE = I_LOAD_PORT AND DESTINATION_PORT_CODE = I_DISCHARGE_PORT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup to get the DESTINATION_DWEL for the STG_COO records matching with MFS_HDR and DTL
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_LEADS_TIMES_DEST_DWELL1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: DC_REGION = I_DC_REGION AND ROUTING_CODE = I_ROUTING_CODE AND ORIGIN_PORT_CODE = I_ORIGIN_PORT_CODE AND DESTINATION_PORT_CODE = I_DESTINATION_PORT_CODE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: lookup on the EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF table to extract the PLANT_CODE and PLANT_NAME coulmns.

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on DAY DIMENSION table to extract the AS_OF_DATE field from table.

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, TRUNC(DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE) as DAY_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION
